      <title>健全的住院医生和贷款人更接近债务交易</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/sound-inpatient-physicians-and-lenders-draw-closer-to-debt-deal</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，Sound InPatient Physicians Inc. 正在与一组债权人就一项交易进行深入讨论，该交易将延长该医院人力资源公司的第一留置权和第二留置权定期贷款的期限，以帮助避免现金短缺。情况。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/sound-inpatient-physicians-and-lenders-draw-closer-to-debt-deal</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 21:12:53 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
