      <title>韦斯多策略对冲基金关闭后申请破产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/weiss-multi-strategy-hedge-fund-files-bankruptcy-after-shutdown</link>
      <description><![CDATA[总部位于纽约的投资管理公司 Weiss Multi-Strategy Advisers LLC 宣布关闭业务约两个月后，该公司申请破产。]]></description>
