    <item>
      <title>布鲁克斯表示，日本的债务困境可能会导致任何外汇干预措施失败</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/japan-s-debt-dilemma-may-doom-any-fx-intervention-brooks-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[对于高盛集团前首席货币策略师罗宾·布鲁克斯来说，日本巨额政府债务——至少现在——任何支撑日元的努力都可能失败。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/japan-s-debt-dilemma-may-doom-any-fx-intervention-brooks-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>加密货币复兴后，香港在比特币 ETF 市场与美国展开竞争</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/hong-kong-debuts-spot-bitcoin-btc-ether-eth-etfs-in-crypto-hub-bet</link>
      <description><![CDATA[一批直接投资加密货币的交易所交易基金将于周二在香港首次亮相，预示着美国比特币产品的潜在竞争，这些产品的受欢迎程度引发了数字资产创纪录的上涨。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-29/hong-kong-debuts-spot-bitcoin-btc-ether-eth-etfs-in-crypto-hub-bet</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 29 Apr 2024 21:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
